光浴。<br />\n十度，法國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人在花園裡種花。<br />\n五度，義大利人發不動車子，西伯利亞人開敞篷車遊街。<br />\n零下五度，加州人凍斃了；西伯利亞人在戶外烤肉。<br />\n零下十度，英國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人開始穿長袖。<br />\n零下五十度，北極熊撤離北極；西伯利亞軍隊延後冬季野外求生訓練，等待真正的冬天到來。<br />\n零下一百八十三度，食物中的微生物死亡；西伯利亞牛隻抱怨酪農的手太冰。<br />\n零下兩百七十三度，原子停止活動；西伯利亞人終於說：『老天，外面好冷！』<br />\n連登仔：『最近天氣開始轉涼了！』"},{"pid":"cda858aabc07f44e8d421fd98f5517c85d4f653a","tid":1766734,"uid":283207,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9e0e6af3c2e8b4295c0566fa3055a3e31395cfc8","tid":1766734,"uid":83523,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T23:11:18.000Z","msg":"濕度百分之55<br />\n<br />\n點會係濕凍呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T23:18:08.000Z","msg":"仲唔濕咩55喎"},{"pid":"0b0bdf47227f96a941d409df495a64f0d1472bd1","tid":1766734,"uid":83523,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cda858aabc07f44e8d421fd98f5517c85d4f653a","tid":1766734,"uid":283207,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9e0e6af3c2e8b4295c0566fa3055a3e31395cfc8","tid":1766734,"uid":83523,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T23:11:18.000Z","msg":"濕度百分之55<br />\n<br />\n點會係濕凍呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T23:18:08.000Z","msg":"仲唔濕咩55喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T23:19:04.000Z","msg":"55係同香港之前幾年比叫乾啦"},{"pid":"48d63a04fcf6e2d6511ec72c6e04523f28217fd7","tid":1766734,"uid":229296,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T23:20:17.000Z","msg":"室外凍過日本唔敢講<br />\n但室內無暖氣真係好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013cce358ef9e8888b2692fff137b8418decf5c2","tid":1766734,"uid":141164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bef1183994f175da4704a528810095034555a104","tid":1766734,"uid":16451,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T23:12:56.000Z","msg":"成班虧佬<img src=\"/assets/face